Born
(1956-04-11) 11 April 1956 (age 61)


Occupation
CEO, Darden Restaurants


Clarence Otis, Jr. (born April 11, 1956 in Vicksburg, Mississippi, United States) is an American businessman and former CEO of Darden Restaurants. Otis was named the 11th most powerful person in Central Florida by the Orlando Sentinel in 2010.[1]



